{
  "stem": "6195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's the first experience, the first bitter experience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were coming into our flat or unit or whatever you prefer to call it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] First they threw out whatever they could of the wardrobes everywhere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother, at that time, wasn't well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Since the minute she saw the people hanging there, she, she broke down, and, and she just couldn't accept it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said then and there, I'm not going to live through that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Is something happening to me?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we called a Jewish doctor, because my uncle already fled to the Russian side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And they didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, she was getting worse from hour to hour.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was very, very sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were giving her injections of morphine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had pains all over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was petrified.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- on both fronts, on my home front, and, and the Nazis around me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were coming and going, and into the flat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They ripped up the parquet floors, looking for valuables.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SIGHS] And they went into the bedroom, saw my mother, and they told her to get up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she was dozing after the morphine, and I said, she can't.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's sick.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They threw her off her bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with their boots, they were trapping on her, and, and just to death.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I didn't realize.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I haven't seen death before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I didn't realize that she's dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I begged them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cried.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I begged.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And each time I opened my mouth, I was getting a slap in the face, a slap in the head, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in the back, and every possible place.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
